# Java Learning Journey

This repository documents my journey learning Java, starting from the fundamentals
to object-oriented programming concepts.

It includes small examples and practice code written to strengthen my understanding
of core Java and backend development basics.

## Topics Covered
- Java basics
- Variables and data types
- Methods
- Arrays
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
- Inheritance

## Project Structure
Each folder represents a specific Java topic or concept with example code.

## About Me
- Software Engineering student
- Interested in backend development
- Languages: Java, C#
- Currently improving Git and GitHub skills
